'''2006年威斯特彻斯特县龙卷风'''是有纪录以来美国[[纽约州|纽约州]][[威斯特彻斯特县|威斯特彻斯特县]]最强烈、规模最大的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]<ref name="THPWest" />，于2006年7月12日在[[纽约州|纽约州]]着陆，然后行进了21[[公里|公里]]进入[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]西南部，一共行经两个州，持续时间为33[[分钟|分钟]]。这场龙卷风于[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]下午15点30分（[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]晚上19点30分）在[[哈德逊河|哈德逊河]]岸着陆，接下来变成[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]前进了5公里穿过该河。上岸后，龙卷风进入威斯特彻斯特县并以[[藤田级数|F1级]]强度袭击了[[斷頭谷_(紐約州)|斷頭谷]]。穿过该镇后，系统增强为F2级龙卷风，直径增大到近400[[米_(单位)|米]]<ref name="MSSum">{{cite web | date = 2006-07-14 | title = Summary of Tornado | publisher = National Weather Service in Upton, New York | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/okx/pns/torjul06.txt | archivedate = 2012-07-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120724073628/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/okx/pns/torjul06.txt | deadurl = no }}</ref>。龙卷风继续穿越该县直至于{{lang|en|[[北美东部时区|EDT]]}}下午16点01分（{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}晚上20点01分）进入康涅狄格州，并很快于{{lang|en|EDT}}下午16点03分（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上20点03分）在该州的[[格林尼治_(康涅狄格州)|格林尼治]]消散<ref name="MSSum" />。这场龙卷风是自1950年以来已知进入威斯特彻斯特县或在该县着陆的第八个龙卷风<ref name="THPWest">{{cite web | author = Storm Prediction Center | year = 2007 | title = Tornado History Project: Westchester, New York Tornadoes, 1950-2007 | publisher = Joshua Lietz (TornadoHistoryProject.com) | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://www.tornadohistoryproject.com/tornado/20060712.36.4/table | archive-date = 2014-01-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106094321/http://www.tornadohistoryproject.com/tornado/20060712.36.4/table | dead-url = no }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。

龙卷风摧毁谷仓和仓库，震碎大型彩绘玻璃窗，许多商铺受损，成千上万的树木连根拔起，经济损失总额约为1210万美元。所幸无人丧生，共六人受伤。

== 气象简介 ==
[[File:July_12,_2006_Westchester_Tornado.gif|thumb]]下午15点45分，[[气象雷达|气象雷达]]显示[[超级单体|超级单体]]生成龙卷风的动画]]
7月12日，[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]东部上空受[[安大略|安大略]]西南部[[低气压|地面低气压区]]影响发展出[[超级单体|超级单体]][[雷暴|雷暴]]。[[三州地区|三州地区]]昼间的炎热天气令系统变得不稳定，这也是发展阵雨和雷阵雨的关键因素。由于这样的环境很有利于龙卷风的发展，[[美国风暴预报中心|美国风暴预报中心]]于[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]中午12点40分（{{lang|en|UTC}}下午16点40分）发布[[龙卷风预警|龙卷风预警]]<ref name="Tornadowatch">{{cite web | author = Thompson | date = 2006-07-12 | title = Severe Weather Watch #593 (Tornado Watch) | publisher = Storm Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | archivedate = 2012-09-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120923065110/http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/watch/2006/ww0593.html | url = http://www.spc.noaa.gov/products/watch/2006/ww0593.html }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[北美东部时区|EDT]]}}下午14点（{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点）左右已形成强烈雷暴，并于{{lang|en|EDT}}下午14点45分（{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点45分）左右在[[博根縣|博根縣]]的[[卡尔士达特|卡尔士达特]]（{{lang|en|Carlstadt}}）附近生成[[漏斗云|漏斗云]]，但没有造成损失<ref name="NJFunnel">{{cite report | author = Stuart Hinson | year = 2006 | title = July 12, Weather Event #625643 (Funnel Cloud) | publisher = National Climatic Data Center}}</ref>。这股风暴在进入纽约州的过程中增强并发展成超级单体<ref name="Tornado1" />，约15分钟后，[[罗克兰县_(纽约州)|罗克兰县]]南部和[[威斯特彻斯特县|威斯特彻斯特县]]收到[[龙卷风警报|龙卷风警报]]并持续到{{lang|en|EDT}}下午16点15分（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上21点15分）<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | date = 2006-07-13 | title = Westchester County Storm: Let The Clean-Up Begin | publisher = WCBS-TV}}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|EDT}}下午15点30分（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上19点30分）左右，一个{{lang|en|F1}}级龙卷风在罗克兰县[[哈德逊河|哈德逊河]]沿岸着陆，风暴宽度为91米，在码头着陆。龙卷风接下来入河变成海龙卷风，然后向斜对岸行进5公里后穿过该河，在[[塔潘奇伊桥|塔潘奇伊桥]]（{{lang|en|Tappan Zee Bridge}}）附近经过后进入威斯特彻斯特县<ref name="Tornado1">{{cite report | author = Stuart Hinson | year = 2006 | title = July 12, Weather Event #626587 (Tornado) | publisher = National Climatic Data Center}}</ref>，成为该县有纪录以来的第八场龙卷风<ref name="THPWest" />。

龙卷风于{{lang|en|EDT}}下午15点37分（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上19点37分）左右袭击断头谷，有报告显示两分钟后龙卷风外围的阵风风速为每小时93公里。系统在接近[[纽约州9A公路|纽约州9A公路]]时达到{{lang|en|F2}}级强度并袭击了一个[[橱柜|橱柜]]公司[[仓库|仓库]]，产生的风速高达每小时253公里，估计有274米宽<ref name="Tornado2">{{cite report | author = Stuart Hinson | year = 2006 | title = July 12, Weather Event #626588 (Tornado) | publisher = National Climatic Data Center}}</ref>，是威斯特彻斯特县有纪录以来最强烈的龙卷风<ref name="USAT">{{cite news | author = Jim Fitzgerald | date = 2006-07-14 | title = Weather Service confirms F-2 tornado roared through N.Y., Conn. on Wednesday | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2006-07-14-ny-tornado-confirmed_x.htm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023022559/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2006-07-14-ny-tornado-confirmed_x.htm }}</ref>，不过之后很快就减弱为{{lang|en|F1}}级强度。随着龙卷风靠近纽约州和康涅狄格州边界，[[瓦尔哈拉_(纽约州)|瓦尔哈拉]]（{{lang|en|Valhalla}}）的[[肯西科水库|肯西科水库]]（{{lang|en|Kensico Reservoir}}）有报告受到轻微损伤。整场风暴在威斯特彻斯特县内行进的路途全长约为13公里<ref name="Tornado2" />。系统经两州边界进入[[費爾菲爾德縣_(康乃狄克州)|費爾菲爾德縣]]后进一步减弱，于{{lang|en|EDT}}下午16点03分（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上20点03分）在格林尼治升空，其在康涅狄格州内行进的距离约为3.2公里。系统之后不久在[[梅里特大道|梅里特大道]]（{{lang|en|Merritt Parkway}}）附近还出现了一次短暂的着陆<ref name="Tornado3">{{cite report | author = Stuart Hinson | year = 2006 | title = July 12, Weather Event #606978 (Tornado) | publisher = National Climatic Data Center}}</ref>。这场龙卷风总计持续了33分钟，行经两个州，行程21公里<ref name="MSSum" />。

== 影响 ==
[[File:2006_Westchester_County_tornado_forrest_damage.jpg|thumb]]造成的损害]]
这场龙卷风行经罗克兰县、威斯特彻斯特县和費爾菲爾德縣，成千上万的树木被刮倒甚至连根拔起，还有多幢建筑物受损，其中一个橱柜公司仓库受到了严重的结构性破坏。报告统计共有6人受伤，经济损失达1210万美元<ref name="MSSum" />。

经报道，罗克兰县遭受轻度损失，有一个码头和一艘小船受损<ref name="MSSum" />。龙卷风穿越哈德逊河后进入威斯特彻斯特县，这里受到的破坏最为严重。断头谷有多家商户和民宅的屋顶受损，壁板被撕裂<ref name="MSSum" />。阿维拉教会圣德勒撒教堂一扇三米高的彩绘[[玻璃|玻璃]]窗被震碎<ref name="USAT" />。然后波坎蒂克山（{{lang|en|Pocantico Hills}}）受到强度达{{lang|en|F2}}级的龙卷风袭击，许多树木被连根拔起，还有两个谷仓被毁。加利福尼亚州橱柜公司的一个仓库受到严重的结构性破坏，两面[[混凝土|混凝土]]墙被毁<ref name="MSSum" />。仓库中的工作人员在龙卷风来袭时用作避难所的楼梯间倒塌，导致4人受伤。建筑物的混凝土块被风吹飞，其中有些击中了附近[[停车场|停车场]]的多辆汽车<ref name="USAT" />。附近一家[[舒适客栈|舒适客栈]]（{{lang|en|Comfort Inn}}）部分屋顶被掀开<ref name="WESH">{{cite web | date = 2006-07-13 | author = Associated Press | title = Tornado Rips Through Suburban New York | publisher = Internet Broadcasting Systems, Inc | accessdate = 2012-02-17 | url = http://www.wesh.com/news/9510358/detail.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217131426/http://www.wesh.com/news/9510358/detail.html | archivedate = 2012-02-17 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。橱柜公司仓库附近的一所[[学校|学校]]在收看龙卷风警报后进行疏散<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news | author = Lisa W. Foderaro | date = 2006-07-13 | title = Tornado in Westchester Tosses Around Trees and Damages Property | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106144622/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/07/13/nyregion/13weather.html?pagewanted=print&_r=0 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/07/13/nyregion/13weather.html?pagewanted=print&_r=0 }}</ref>。

[[File:Westchester_Tornado_damage1.JPG|thumb]]

龙卷风穿过纽约州{{lang|en|9A}}公路时将一辆州警用车抬起并连续翻滚了好几圈才倒在地上，幸运的是车内警员只受了轻伤<ref name="USAT" />。风暴朝东北偏北方向行进并袭击了芒特普莱森特（{{lang|en|Mount Pleasant}}）和[[霍桑_(纽约州)|霍桑]]，许多树木受损，并有部分建筑受到轻微的结构性损伤<ref name="MSSum" />。[[锯木厂河滨大道|锯木厂河滨大道]]沿途受到的损害迫使官员关闭了芒特普莱森特附近的一段[[高速公路|高速公路]]<ref name="CNN">{{cite news |author=Rose Arce |date=2006-07-13 |title=Tornado hits north of Manhattan, Winds damage store, close highway; no serious injuries reported |publisher=Cable News Network |accessdate=2015-02-16 |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2006/WEATHER/07/12/ny.tornado/index.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081104224713/http://www.cnn.com/2006/WEATHER/07/12/ny.tornado/index.html |archivedate=2008-11-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。树木倒在街道和[[铁轨|铁轨]]上，[[大都會北方鐵路|大都會北方鐵路]]因此必须中止运营，导致严重的交通延误<ref name="NYTimes" />。龙卷风接下来经过瓦尔哈拉的肯西科水库后进入康涅狄格州<ref name="MSSum" />，刮倒了多条电线杆，导致近万居民家中停电<ref name="USAT" />。这场龙卷风共导致纽约州6人轻伤，经济损失共计1010万美元<ref name="Tornado2" />。

进入康涅狄格州費爾菲爾德縣小镇格林尼治后龙卷风进一步减弱，但其在该州行进的3.2公里路程上还是拔起或折断了数以千计的树木。多幢建筑物受到轻度损伤<ref name="MSSum" />，整个格林尼治有1700位居民家中停电，六条道路被阻塞。受损的区域主要集中在小镇的西北部<ref name="NYTimes2">{{cite news | author = Avi Salzman and Anahad O'Connor | date = 2006-07-16 | title = The Week; Rare Tornado Snaps Trees and Power Lines | publisher = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F04E2D91F30F935A25754C0A9609C8B63 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131205035319/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9F04E2D91F30F935A25754C0A9609C8B63 | archivedate = 2013-12-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。该州共计受到的经济损失数额为200万美元<ref name="Tornado3" />。

== 余波 ==
龙卷风过后，断头谷市长宣布全镇范围进入紧急状态<ref name="ABC7">{{cite news | author = Eyewitness News | date = 2006-07-13 | title = Weather Service confirms F2 tornado in area, Sleepy Hollow, Hawthorne hardest hit | publisher = ABC News | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | archivedate = 2012-09-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120925004255/http://abclocal.go.com/wabc/story?section=weather&id=4363255 | url = http://abclocal.go.com/wabc/story?section=weather&id=4363255 }}</ref>。两百名急救人员对这场风暴作出响应<ref name="LoHUD2">{{cite news | author = Reka Bala and Glenn Blain | date = 2006-07-13 | title = Tornado slams Lower Hudson Valley | publisher = The Journal News | accessdate = 2014-01-06 | archivedate = 2012-03-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120328190306/http://www.lohud.com/article/20060713/NEWS09/607130345 | url = http://www.lohud.com/article/20060713/NEWS09/607130345?nclick_check=1 }}</ref>。[[聯合愛迪生電力公司|聯合愛迪生電力公司]]（{{lang|en|Consolidated Edison}}）派工作人员前往修复倒塌的电线杆，恢复道路畅通。次日晚上，威斯特彻斯特县原本一万户停电的居民家中已经基本恢复，只有600户尚未通电<ref name="USAT" />。该县还在风暴过后开放了紧急行动中心加以响应<ref>{{cite news | date = 2006-07-13 | title = Tornado hits north of Manhattan | publisher = CNN | accessdate = 2011-12-09 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2006/WEATHER/07/12/ny.tornado/index.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106221327/http://edition.cnn.com/2006/WEATHER/07/12/ny.tornado/index.html | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。龙卷风过去两天后，大部分道路都已畅销，所有地区的供电都已恢复。不过位于[[柏油村_(紐約州)|柏油村]]的一条休闲小径因有多棵树木倒塌，预计还需再过两个[[星期|星期]]才能开放<ref name="LoHUD">{{cite web |date=2006-07-15 |author=Candice Ferrette |title=Westchester tornado twists many lives |publisher=The Journal News |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archivedate=2012-02-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229100327/http://www.lohud.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060715%2FNEWS02%2F607150347 |url=http://www.lohud.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060715/NEWS02/607150347 }}</ref>。大都會北方鐵路将前往上哈林区的线路列车暂停运营至{{lang|en|EDT}}下午17点（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上21点）以便清除铁轨上的瓦砾，之前已经上车的旅客则由客车转送至目的地<ref name="NYTimes" />。到了{{lang|en|EDT}}晚上19点（{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上23点），所有列车都已恢复运营<ref name="LoHUD2" />。

